同时支持使用post或get查询
查询指定高度或hash的区块
参数：二者选其一
hash: 区块hash
height:区块高度
如果hash和height都是有效值时，则可能返回两个区块，当二者都指向一个区块时，则返回一个区块

*****
The GraphQl query for this endpoint is:
``` graphql
query block_detail ($height: bigint! = "0", $hash: String = "") {
  block(where: {_or:[{height:{_eq:$height}},{hash:{_eq:$hash}}]}) {
    height
    num_txs
    timestamp
    reward
    total_gas
    hash
    proposer_address
    validator_info {
      self_delegate_address
      consensus_address
      operator_address
    }
    validator_description {
      moniker
    }
    reward_allocates {
      region_id
      region_treasury_address
      gag_coins
      gea_coins
    }
    gas_fee {
      fee_denom
      total_fee
    }
    raw_log {
      block
      log
    }
  }
}

```

